        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued August 1 at 10:10PM MDT until August 1 at 10:30PM MDT by NWS Great Falls MT</headline>
        <description>At 1010 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 22 miles southwest
of Fort Belknap, or 22 miles south of Chinook, moving north at 15
mph.

HAZARD...Quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Damage to vehicles is expected.

Locations impacted include...
Cleveland.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
